&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://i.imgur.com/8Crue8E.png?1&quot; alt=&quot;Imgur&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html">學習 Ext JS 筆記．</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">使用 Packer 建立 Windows VM box</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/devops/2016/05/06/learn-packer-to-build-windows-vm.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="使用 Packer 建立 Windows VM box" /><published>2016-05-06T17:30:00+08:00</published><updated>2016-05-06T17:30:00+08:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/devops/2016/05/06/learn-packer-to-build-windows-vm</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/devops/2016/05/06/learn-packer-to-build-windows-vm.html">&lt;p&gt;學習 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.packer.io/&quot;&gt;Packer&lt;/a&gt; 筆記．(不完整版)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;安裝&quot;&gt;安裝&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;參閱官方&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.packer.io/docs/installation.html&quot;&gt;文件&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;實作-windows&quot;&gt;實作 Windows&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://stefanscherer.github.io/setup-local-windows-2016-tp5-docker-vm/&quot;&gt;Setup a local Windows 2016 TP5 Docker VM&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

